<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>WanderWell — 604 Downstairs | Waianae, Hawaiʻi</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,700;1,9..144,300&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"/>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --brand: #367bbf;
    --brand-dark: #1e4e7a;
    --brand-light: #e8f2fb;
    --sand: #f8f4ee;
    --bark: #3a2e24;
    --ocean: #0d4f78;
    --foam: #ffffff;
    --mist: #f0f4f8;
    --leaf: #2d7a52;
    --sun: #f5a623;
    --warn: #fff8dc;
    --warn-border: #f5a623;
    --radius: 16px;
    --shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    --shadow-lg: 0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--sand);
    color: var(--bark);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  h1,h2,h3,h4 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-weight: 500; }

  /* ───────── HERO ───────── */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--ocean) 0%, var(--brand) 60%, #4aa3e0 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 72px 24px 80px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Ccircle cx='30' cy='30' r='20'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: #b8ddff; }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
  }
  .hero-chips {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .chip {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ───────── LAYOUT ───────── */
  .container { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  section { padding: 56px 0; }
  section + section { border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--brand);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
    color: var(--bark);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  /* ───────── CARDS ───────── */
  .card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card-inner { padding: 28px 32px; }
  .card img { width: 100%; height: 220px; object-fit: cover; display: block; }

  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
  @media(max-width: 640px) {
    .grid-2, .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ───────── CHECK-IN ───────── */
  .checkin-times {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .time-box {
    background: var(--brand-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .time-box .label { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--brand); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .time-box .time { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--ocean); line-height: 1; }
  .time-box .note { font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 4px; }

  .address-box {
    background: var(--bark);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .address-box .label { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; opacity: 0.6; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .address-box p { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .address-box small { opacity: 0.65; font-size: 13px; }

  /* ───────── PHOTO STRIP ───────── */
  .photo-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .photo-strip img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; display: block; border-radius: 10px; }
  @media(max-width: 640px) {
    .photo-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .photo-strip img:first-child { grid-column: 1/-1; height: 180px; }
  }

  /* ───────── STEPS ───────── */
  .steps { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; margin: 20px 0; }
  .steps li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: var(--mist);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .step-num {
    background: var(--brand);
    color: white;
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .steps li p { font-size: 14px; }
  .steps li strong { color: var(--bark); }

  /* ───────── PHOTO PAIR ───────── */
  .photo-pair {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }
  .photo-pair figure { position: relative; }
  .photo-pair img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px; display: block; }
  .photo-pair figcaption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.65), transparent);
    color: white;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 16px 14px 10px;
    border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 480px) { .photo-pair { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* ───────── CODE BOX ───────── */
  .code-block {
    background: var(--ocean);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 18px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .code-block .code-label { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; opacity: 0.7; }
  .code-block .code-val { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 2.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  .code-block .code-icon { font-size: 2rem; opacity: 0.4; }

  /* ───────── AMENITIES ───────── */
  .amenity-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .amenity-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--brand);
  }
  .amenity-card .icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .amenity-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--ocean); }
  .amenity-card p { font-size: 13.5px; color: #555; }
  .amenity-card .highlight {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--brand-light);
    color: var(--brand-dark);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 480px) { .amenity-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* ───────── RULES / NOTES ───────── */
  .note-box {
    background: var(--warn);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--warn-border);
    border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .note-box strong { color: #a06000; }

  /* ───────── VOLUNTEER SECTION ───────── */
  .volunteer-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d4f78 0%, #1a7a4a 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 48px 32px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .volunteer-hero h2 { font-size: 1.9rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .volunteer-hero p { opacity: 0.85; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .value-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 14px; margin: 32px 0; }
  .value-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--brand);
  }
  .value-card .v-icon { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .value-card h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--brand-dark); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .value-card p { font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  @media(max-width: 640px) { .value-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

  /* ───────── MAP LAYOUT ───────── */
  .map-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    height: 500px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    margin: 32px 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .map-sidebar {
    background: var(--bark);
    color: white;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .map-sidebar h3 { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.6; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .sidebar-pin {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 10px 8px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  .sidebar-pin:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .sidebar-pin .pin-dot {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .sidebar-pin .pin-home { background: #1e3a5f; border: 2px solid white; }
  .sidebar-pin .pin-org { background: #2d7a52; }
  .sidebar-pin strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; line-height: 1.3; }
  .sidebar-pin span { opacity: 0.65; font-size: 11px; }
  #vol-map { flex: 1; }
  @media(max-width: 640px) {
    .map-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; height: auto; }
    .map-sidebar { height: 220px; }
    #vol-map { height: 320px; }
  }

  /* ───────── ORG CARDS ───────── */
  .category-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 36px 0 16px;
  }
  .category-label .cat-icon { font-size: 20px; }
  .category-label h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--ocean); }

  .org-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .org-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 22px 24px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--leaf);
  }
  .org-card h4 { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--bark); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .org-card .org-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--brand); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .org-card .org-who, .org-card .org-what { font-size: 13px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .org-card .org-who strong, .org-card .org-what strong { color: var(--bark); }
  .org-card .org-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--brand);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .org-card .org-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .org-card .org-note {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    background: var(--brand-light);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    color: var(--ocean);
  }
  @media(max-width: 640px) { .org-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* ───────── CHECKOUT ───────── */
  .checklist { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .checklist li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .check-icon {
    width: 24px; height: 24px;
    background: var(--leaf);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  /* ───────── THANK YOU ───────── */
  .thankyou {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand) 0%, var(--ocean) 100%);
    color: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 48px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .thankyou h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .thankyou p { opacity: 0.88; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 20px; }
  .hashtag { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-style: italic; opacity: 0.75; }
  .host-sig { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.7; }
  .host-sig strong { display: block; font-size: 15px; opacity: 1; margin-top: 4px; }

  /* ───────── DIVIDER ───────── */
  .wave-divider { text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem; opacity: 0.18; letter-spacing: 0.3em; padding: 8px 0; }

  /* ───────── PRINT ───────── */
  @media print {
    .hero { background: var(--ocean) !important; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; }
    .map-layout { height: 360px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════ HERO ═══════════════════════════ -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">🌺 WanderWell Welcome Letter</div>
  <h1>Aloha, and welcome to<br><em>604 Downstairs</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Your home away from home on Oʻahu's beautiful west side — right across from Pokai Bay Beach Park.</p>
  <div class="hero-chips">
    <span class="chip">📍 Waiʻanae, Oʻahu</span>
    <span class="chip">🏡 Downstairs Unit</span>
    <span class="chip">🌊 Steps from the Beach</span>
    <span class="chip">🤙 Host: DeBora</span>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="container">

<!-- ═══════════════════════════ CHECK-IN / CHECK-OUT ═══════════════════════════ -->
<section id="checkin">
  <div class="section-label">Arrival &amp; Departure</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Check-In &amp; Check-Out</h2>

  <div class="checkin-times">
    <div class="time-box">
      <div class="label">Check-In</div>
      <div class="time" style="color:var(--leaf)">Flexible</div>
      <div class="note">Codes sent morning of arrival</div>
    </div>
    <div class="time-box">
      <div class="label">Check-Out</div>
      <div class="time">10:30<span style="font-size:1.1rem">AM</span></div>
      <div class="note">Please notify host if earlier</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="address-box">
    <div class="label">Property Address</div>
    <p>85-043 Waianae Valley Road, Waiʻanae, HI 96792</p>
    <small>📌 For GPS — use <strong>"Pokai Bay Beach Park"</strong> to navigate here. Look for the Gray/White two-story unit. Your unit is the downstairs unit to the far left.</small>
  </div>

  <div class="photo-strip">
    <img src="https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/4tZ52HuuLaqYvrrq0Pkn/media/69cd1da4d11b2d53c57c3217.png" alt="The Unit" />
    <img src="https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/4tZ52HuuLaqYvrrq0Pkn/media/69cd1da4e9047b61f58b45dc.png" alt="The Unit" />
    <img src="https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/4tZ52HuuLaqYvrrq0Pkn/media/69cd1da445ec94311dee8828.png" alt="The Unit" />
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════ ACCESS & ENTRY ═══════════════════════════ -->
<section id="access">
  <div class="section-label">Getting In</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Access &amp; Entry</h2>

  <p style="margin-bottom:20px">Your key will be in the lockbox on the black rod iron gate. Here's everything you need to get in smoothly.</p>

  <div class="code-block">
    <div>
      <div class="code-label">🔒 Lockbox Code</div>
      <div class="code-val">5150</div>
    </div>
    <div class="code-icon">🗝</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="steps">
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <p><strong>Find the lockbox:</strong> Facing the driveway from the outside — look to your <strong>LEFT</strong> side, then down. The lockbox is on the lower area of the black rod iron gate.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <p><strong>Retrieve your keys:</strong> The <strong>larger key</strong> is for the front door. The <strong>smaller key</strong> is for the gate. We currently have only one set — please do not lose or misplace them (a replacement fee will apply).</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <p><strong>Enter the driveway:</strong> Walk inside the driveway. Your front door is straight ahead — the only front door in this driveway area.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <p><strong>Open the front door:</strong> Lift the door handle <strong>UP</strong> until you hear a click. Then use the key to unlock. There's a slight step up, then stairs leading up into the unit.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">5</div>
      <p><strong>Locking from inside:</strong> Same process — lift the handle up and turn the knob. No key needed from the inside.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="note-box">
    <strong>🚪 Tip:</strong> It may take a few tries — hold the handle up and use the key simultaneously. You've got this!
  </div>

  <div class="photo-pair">
    <figure>
      <img src="https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/4tZ52HuuLaqYvrrq0Pkn/media/69cd1da4aa4c650c9f152e9c.png" alt="The Gate" />
      <figcaption>The Gate</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure>
      <img src="https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/4tZ52HuuLaqYvrrq0Pkn/media/69cd1da4eaf7fd11f32becaf.png" alt="Lockbox" />
      <figcaption>Lockbox Location</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════ PARKING ═══════════════════════════ -->
<section id="parking">
  <div class="section-label">Parking</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Parking Instructions</h2>

  <div class="card">
    <img src="https://assets.cdn.filesafe.space/4tZ52HuuLaqYvrrq0Pkn/media/69cd1fb2eaf7fd6f802c253d.png" alt="Front door and driveway" />
    <div class="card-inner">
      <p>You are welcome to <strong>park in the driveway</strong> upon arrival.</p>
      <br>
      <div class="note-box">
        <strong>🚗 Gate Rule:</strong> Please close the gate each time anyone exits — even just to cross the street. No need to fully lock for short trips, just loop the lock through. If leaving for the day, please lock completely.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════ UNIT DIRECTIONS ═══════════════════════════ -->
<section id="unit">
  <div class="section-label">Finding Your Unit</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Unit Directions</h2>

  <p style="margin-bottom:20px">This is a two-story property. <strong>Your unit is the downstairs unit</strong> to the far left when facing the building from the street. Look for the wood bench by the front door.</p>

  <ul class="steps">
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <p><strong>Enter the driveway:</strong> Once inside the gate, walk straight ahead toward the front of the building.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <p><strong>Find the walkway:</strong> There's a walkway by the front lawn — make a quick left, then it's the <strong>1st door on the right-hand side</strong>.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <p><strong>Sliding glass door:</strong> The sliding glass door is to the LEFT of the front door — both lead into your unit.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <p><strong>Watch your step:</strong> There's a slight step up and stairs that lead up to the living area inside.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════ AMENITIES ═══════════════════════════ -->
<section id="amenities">
  <div class="section-label">What's Inside</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">Unit Amenities &amp; Guidelines</h2>

  <div class="amenity-grid">
    <div class="amenity-card">
      <div class="icon">📶</div>
      <h3>WiFi</h3>
      <p>Stay connected throughout your stay with high-speed internet.</p>
      <div class="highlight">Network: SpectrumSetup-E5</div><br>
      <div class="highlight">Password: modernbike710</div>
